{"tid":2075690,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅：中美貿易協議已「完結」","createTime":"2020-06-23T04:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:50:14.000Z","uid":53844,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a35e24ec6475dd510ad62f5a8abd67f6e759394","tid":2075690,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"白宮貿易顧問稱中美貿易協議已「完結」<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，中美貿易協議的轉捩點在於中方延誤通報疫情。納瓦羅指，美中雙方在今年1月15日簽署貿易協議後，美方才知道疫情擴散情況。<br />\n<br />\n中美過去先後就疫情、香港等事務問題上導致關係緊張。美國總統特朗普日前認為，自己達成一份非常好的協議，中方正購買很多美國貨，可能會購買總值2500億美元的美國商品。<br />\n<br />\n他又承認，推遲制裁打壓新疆維吾爾人的中國官員，是為了避免影響中美貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-23 10:00:45"},{"pid":"a2f34418880ea4ac54bed1f4a7002a85dbf0d653","tid":2075690,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6b19c5ce5bdfc865e14c4febd7b04bd3ba6cbf","tid":2075690,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:26:51.000Z","msg":"即係中共又毀約，唔俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1384e749855851f4ccb5d2a2a55dc54b904ff41","tid":2075690,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"納瓦羅話左係FAKE NEWS  被左媒曲解了"},{"pid":"49c9400e5d6ec2e072264966c764355173e7fd1c","tid":2075690,"uid":333580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"拿華路就拿華路啦"},{"pid":"45c450b28a70e9178ef4c6185d45ca91bd3939b2","tid":2075690,"uid":183685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor